<view class="page data-v-132d2ab4"><view class="card data-v-132d2ab4"><view class="section-title data-v-132d2ab4">上传衣物照片</view><button type="primary" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['chooseAndUpload',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-132d2ab4">选择并上传</button><view class="tip data-v-132d2ab4">支持相册/拍照，上传后会自动识别类别和描述。</view></view><block wx:if="{{result}}"><view class="card data-v-132d2ab4"><view class="section-title data-v-132d2ab4">识别结果</view><view class="line data-v-132d2ab4">{{"名称："+result.item}}</view><view class="line data-v-132d2ab4">{{"类别："+result.category}}</view><view class="line data-v-132d2ab4">{{"描述："+(result.description||'无')}}</view><block wx:if="{{result.image_url}}"><image class="preview data-v-132d2ab4" src="{{result.image_url}}" mode="widthFix"></image></block></view></block></view>